### STEP 2: The License (`LICENSE`) ‚öñÔ∏è

Your audit strongly recommends the **GNU GPL v3** license to build trust[cite: 1282].

1.  Create a file named **`LICENSE`** (no extension) in the root folder.
2.  Copy the full text of the GPL v3 license.
    * You can copy the text from here: [Official GPLv3 Text](https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt).

